# 4. Keep your credentials secure and private
# 5. Update .gitignore to exclude .env files
#
# Required minimum setup:
# - TELEGRAM_API_ID and TELEGRAM_API_HASH
# - BOT_TOKEN or SESSION_STRING (for user bot mode)
# - PHONE_NUMBER (if using session generator)
# - FOUNDER_ID
# - LOG_GROUP_ID (for logging)

# Session Generation:
# Run: python3 generate_session.py
# This will automatically generate SESSION_STRING using your API credentials
